						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in front of the Chennakēśavasvāmin temple.</p>						

						<p>Sadāśiva, 1548 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1470, Kīlaka, Pushya ba. 15</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1548 A.D., December 30, (Sunday).</hi></p>						

						<p>It registers a gift of money to the deities Sōmēśvara and Chennakēśava of the village Vōḍigipalli by Sūraparāju Narasarāju for the merit of the twenty four families of the <hi rend="italic">dommari</hi> community to which he apparently belonged.</p>						

						</summary>
